VolWheel

For help on how to use VolWheel, type 'volwheel --help'.

You can track this software on http://oliwer.net/


Requierements
 * Perl 5
 * Gtk2 perl module
 * Gtk2::TrayIcon perl module
 * alsa-utils (for amixer)

Installation
 * Copy volwheel somewhere in your path
 * Copy volwheel.png in /usr/share/pixmaps/
 * You're done.
